If the chain is:

User
  has_many :bookings
Booking
  belongs_to :show
Show
  belongs_to :movie
Movie
  has_one :demo
Demo
  has_one :penguin


Then your nested includes would look like this:

User.includes(
  bookings: {
    show: {
      movie: {
        demo: :penguin
      }
    }
  }
)

