This eagerly loads:

User
  â†’ bookings
    â†’ show
      â†’ movie
        â†’ demo
          â†’ penguin


So accessing:

user.bookings.first.show.movie.demo.penguin


wonâ€™t cause N+1 queries.

ðŸ’¡ General Rule

Just keep nesting hashes following the association chain:

parent.includes(child: { grandchild: { great_grandchild: :next } })